desc: Our human-grade, healthy dog treats are 100% natural, made from 6 simple ingredients. All Wagster Dog Treats proceeds support nonprofit job-training programs.

layout.text: Wagster Treats are hand-made by our dog-loving bakers in California and are full of healthy goodness with none of the artificial additives found in other dog treats. Plus, our bakers use human-grade, vegan ingredients in chef-inspired recipes to create gourmet flavors that dogs will love while learning important skills to change their lives for a brighter future. Order some Wagster Treats online today!
All-natural ingredients that are good for your dog.
Our dog-loving bakers are improving their lives with every batch.
100% of profits support nonprofit job-training programs.
